      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: #ffffff;\">Added</h3>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-41298\">​</a><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-36170\">LCD-36170</a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-41208\">LCD-41208</a>, <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44365\">LCD-44365</a></span>, <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-44731\">LCD-44731</a> - Quality of life improvements for dealing with marketplace apps in the cloud console:</strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> Several quality of life improvements to improve the management, reinstallation and deletion of marketplace apps in the cloud console. These allow for a more pleasant and streamlined user experience that requires way less back and forth between the cloud console and the marketplace.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: #ffffff;\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-45397\">LCD-45397</a><span> </span>- Bug on failing to update Jenkins version:<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> </span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Fixed a bug for customers having issues to update their Jenkins version from a pre 6.0.0 version to 6.0.1-rc2. Allowing customers to leverage new Jenkins functionalities from the more recent versions.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>"
      },
